Results.ReviewText:
I bought this coffee recently. and on breaking the seal, that wonderful coffee aroma 
assailed my senses.  The taste is what real coffee should be.  We invite friends 
to come and enjoy a drink of it.
Results.Title: That Heavenly coffee aroma on opening the jar.

Results.ReviewText: Looking for my normal decaff spotted the Nescafe gold blend decaff,decided to try it..No regrets it is decaffe without any loss of taste and flavour..I think I will retire with this choice..Happy man..
Results.Title: why nescafe is No1..

Results.ReviewText: Good quality but only drink if there is no caffeinated do not like decaffeinated as a rule but taste is still good and I think it is still good value for money if that's the type of coffee you prefer.
Results.Title: Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff

Results.ReviewText: I have bought this on a couple of occasions and have not been disappointed. It is a great flavour, does not need more than a level spoonful per cup and dissolves quickly. As good as percolated coffee.
Results.Title: Great taste!

Results.ReviewText: I have recently tried Gold Blend Decaf and o am really pleased that I did.  It has a rich, smooth taste and is equally as good if not better than similar products.  I would definitely recommend it.
Results.Title: Rich and Smooth

Results.ReviewText: I've drunk nothing but Kenco Decaff for many years but was very impressed with Nescafé Decaff at a friend's home recently. It's flavoursome but not bitter, and I wouldn't hesitate to recommend it.
Results.Title: Real coffee taste without the caffeine!

Results.ReviewText: I used to drink gold blend but the caffeine keeps me awake, I now drink the normal until lunchtime and then switch to decaf for the afternoon/evening. Also have the latte to go cups- delicious!
Results.Title: Love the new look.

Results.ReviewText: I always have a decaf before bed, I like it to taste like coffee without being too strong and bitter. Nescafé ticks all the boxes, I have tried others but find this is the best value for money!
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: Just started drinking decaff and really cannot tell the difference, a smooth rounded taste and no bitter aftertaste (I drink  mine black), if you want to swap to decaff this is the one to try.
Results.Title: Great taste decaff!

Results.ReviewText:
I have just starting drinking decaf coffee and this product was a revelation!
Smooth, not harsh and all the pleasure of a standard coffee without the caffeine!
Very surprised and delighted!
Results.Title: Really smooth and you'd never know it was decaf!

Results.ReviewText: The only Decaff coffee that I can drink without any problems, some bring my mouth up in little blisters. But this has always been good. So I would recommend it to all who have to have Decaff.
Results.Title: Have used Nescafe Gold Decaff for years

Results.ReviewText: I have recently switched to decaf on Doctors orders. Tried some that were really from then discovered Nescafe GOLD decaf. Lovely rounded smooth taste. Can't imagine drinking anything else now
Results.Title: Better than the rest!

Results.ReviewText: Although I rarely drink decaffinated coffee, I buy this one for others. When I do have it I think it compares very well with other good decaff solubles on the market in the same price bracket
Results.Title: A good quality product

Results.ReviewText:
I am now using my second jar of Nescafé Gold Decaff.
It tastes even better than the previous blend,I think the added fine ground beans add a greater depth of flavour.
Well done Nescafé!!
Results.Title: Delicious

Results.ReviewText:
Who would have thought that you could improve on perfection!
Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff has always been the best tasting decaff in the world - and now it's even tastier. Well done Nescafe!
Results.Title: Perfection perfected.

Results.ReviewText: Tried this last week, amazing aroma when you open the jar and the taste is fab. just like fresh ground coffee. Being decaff does not detract from the taste like some others I have tried.
Results.Title: Aroma

Results.ReviewText: Hmmm, a beautiful coffee, smooth full bodied aroma - perfect hug in a cup!  I've recently changed to decaf and couldn't be happier with this product.  I would highly recommended thanks
Results.Title: Hug in a cup!

Results.ReviewText: I bought it last week and I have to say that it taste really nice. All the taste of coffee without the caffeine. I tricked the hubby to taste it and he thought it was his usual coffe.
Results.Title: Intense flavour

Results.ReviewText: I recently started drinking Decaff coffee and I found this to be a lovely flavour whereby you can't tell it is Decaff.  Smooth tasting without any bitter afer taste.  Just delicious!
Results.Title: Delicious coffee

Results.ReviewText: Looked for the blue lid, found new jar love the contents.  Stock up when the offers are on. Drink about 8 beakers a day. Will continue buying.Will keep my eyes open for refill packs.
Results.Title: Missed the blue lid

Results.ReviewText: This is a delicious tasting decaff coffee. It is full of flavour and taste just as good as normal coffee. I would recommend this to anyone. Such great quality at an affordable price.
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: My husband will only drink Nescafe coffee and has done so for over 30 years!  I noticed the gold packaging straight away and my husband reckons it tastes even better. He loves it!
Results.Title: Superb gold packaging!

Results.ReviewText: I bought this as i have recently decided to change to decaf on all drinks i have  it is really lovely no bitter taste and just right without milk if people decide not to take milk
Results.Title: Really lovely taste

Results.ReviewText: Satisfying without the caffeine buzz or effects, that's exactly what I want. A late night cup of Gold that relaxes me and let's me go to rest. Yet it still tastes the best. Bravo!
Results.Title: More with Less!

Results.ReviewText: I always buy decafe but this new blend leaves sediment in the bottom of my cup. I have tried doing the water at different temperatures but to no avail still get the same problem.
Results.Title: Average

Results.ReviewText: I bought this as we cannot have caffeine in our diet.  I thought that the taste may be compromised as there was no caffeine but it was just as rounded a taste as ordinary coffee.
Results.Title: Great taste without the caffeine

Results.ReviewText: This is a lovely coffee. I drink decaf always and this is the best one I have ever tried. Smooth tasting, no bitter aftertaste, and very Moorish. I will keep to this product now.
Results.Title: Lovely warm taste

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is the best decaf you can buy. I did try the store's own but ended up throwing it away as it was bitter. Nescafe Gold is perfect and always gives a great tasting cup.
Results.Title: BEST TASTE, BEST VALUE

Results.ReviewText: The look and feel of the new jar made us want to try it and oh boy, what beautiful coffee! I don't know how they do it but, the flavour is surprisingly like ground coffee - Yum!
Results.Title: Mmmmm - Just like ground coffee!

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff tastes as good as the caffeinated version. Of course, you don't get the caffeine kick, but I switch to this mid-afternoon so that I can sleep at night!
Results.Title: Tastes as good as the caffeinated version
